# .dev.vars.example — TEMPLATE ONLY (safe to commit; contains no real secrets)
#
# To use:  copy this file to ".dev.vars"  (which is git-ignored — never committed)
# then paste real keys into .dev.vars.  NEVER put real keys in this .example file,
# in chat, or anywhere that gets committed.
#
# For production secrets the Worker uses at runtime, prefer:
#   npx wrangler secret put STREET_API_TOKEN
#
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Street.co.uk — Settings > Account Administration > Applications
# Open API token (full access)
STREET_API_TOKEN=""
# Property Feed token (read-only listings, for the website)
STREET_PROPERTY_FEED_TOKEN=""

# A random string YOU choose (e.g. a UUID) — gates the /api/street/ping test route
STREET_TEST_KEY=""

# PayProp — request API access from PayProp (CLIENT MONEY: read/sandbox only; never move funds)
PAYPROP_API_KEY=""

# Fixflo — Settings > API / Integrations > generate API key
FIXFLO_API_KEY=""

# Goodlord — API key for the Street sync
GOODLORD_API_KEY=""

# DocuSign — Admin > Apps & Keys > Integration Key
DOCUSIGN_INTEGRATION_KEY=""
